Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:09.41,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然并没有那么强大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:12.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Pure Purepa-redo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:15.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}总有一天会逮到你
